.TH "drm_sched_suspend_timeout" 9 "drm_sched_suspend_timeout" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_sched_suspend_timeout \- Suspend scheduler job timeout
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned long" drm_sched_suspend_timeout
.BI "(struct drm_gpu_scheduler *sched "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sched" 12
scheduler instance for which to suspend the timeout
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Suspend the delayed work timeout for the scheduler. This is done by
modifying the delayed work timeout to an arbitrary large value,
MAX_SCHEDULE_TIMEOUT in this case.

Returns the timeout remaining
